486
00:36:44,244 --> 00:36:46,246
<i>Heading downstairs to the kitchen.</i>

487
00:36:46,330 --> 00:36:50,959
<i>Getting himself a midnight snack,
and I can guess what kind.</i>

488
00:37:04,973 --> 00:37:07,601
Come on, you son of a bitch.

489
00:37:08,101 --> 00:37:10,437
Damn, he's slick.

490
00:37:22,491 --> 00:37:24,951
