492
00:37:31,875 --> 00:37:36,046
I got you, you little bastard.
Let's see you hop around now.

493
00:37:40,008 --> 00:37:44,930
<i>I try to slow my heart down
and breathe the fire out of my lungs.</i>

494
00:37:45,013 --> 00:37:48,600
<i>My muscles make me
a thousand promises of pain to come.</i>

495
00:37:48,683 --> 00:37:52,521
Let me do it, Marv.
She was my sister. Let me finish him.

496
00:37:52,604 --> 00:37:55,148
You wasn't supposed
to come down here, Wendy.

497
00:37:55,232 --> 00:37:57,943
Oh, but I want to...

498
00:37:58,026 --> 00:38:02,280
<i>I'm sorry, kid, but I haven't
even started with this creep,</i>

499
00:38:02,364 --> 00:38:06,451
