that friend of yours to come running.

508
00:38:40,152 --> 00:38:41,862
Well, what do you know?

509
00:38:42,821 --> 00:38:45,282
Look who's here.

510
00:38:45,365 --> 00:38:46,867
Here he comes.

511
00:38:53,748 --> 00:38:56,293
That's a good dog.

512
00:38:56,376 --> 00:39:00,464
<i>He doesn't scream,
not even when the mutt's had its fill</i>

513
00:39:00,547 --> 00:39:03,133
<i>and Kevin's guts
are lying all over the place.</i>

514
00:39:03,216 --> 00:39:07,262
<i>Somehow the bastard is still alive,
still staring at me.</i>

515
00:39:07,345 --> 00:39:11,266
<i>Not even when I grab the saw
and finish the job.</i>

516
00:39:11,349 --> 00:39:14,436
<i>He never screams.</i>

517
00:39:17,314 --> 00:39:20,525
<i>I put in a call to Kadie's
and ask Nancy to get her clothes on</i>

518
00:39:20,609 --> 00:39:24,029
