523
00:39:35,540 --> 00:39:37,876
<i>and I straightened him out but good.</i>

524
00:39:37,959 --> 00:39:41,630
<i>It really gets my go at
when guys rough up dames.</i>

525
00:39:41,713 --> 00:39:43,465
