526
00:39:43,548 --> 00:39:48,178
Well, your best bet is
drive her all the way up to Sacred Oaks.

527
00:39:48,261 --> 00:39:51,348
What about you?
Are you leaving town?

528
00:39:51,431 --> 00:39:54,184
Hell, no. I like it here.

529
00:39:57,145 --> 00:39:59,981
<i>I hot-wire a parked cab
and stay under the speed limit</i>

530
00:40:00,065 --> 00:40:02,317
<i>so as not to get any attention.</i>

531
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:06,655
<i>My head starts to clear.
