550
00:41:32,574 --> 00:41:35,327
Tormented by guilt.

551
00:41:36,244 --> 00:41:38,621
I tried to counsel him.

552
00:41:40,165 --> 00:41:44,502
But the eating,
it filled him with white light.

553
00:41:44,586 --> 00:41:49,716
Tearful, he swore to me
that he felt the touch of God Almighty.

554
00:41:50,592 --> 00:41:52,677
What the hell do you know?

555
00:41:52,761 --> 00:41:55,305
I know it's pretty
damn weird to eat people.

556
00:41:55,388 --> 00:41:58,183
He didn't just eat their bodies,

557
00:41:58,266 --> 00:42:01,019
