558
00:42:02,604 --> 00:42:04,898
And I joined in.

559
00:42:08,276 --> 00:42:10,445
They were all whores.

560
00:42:11,613 --> 00:42:15,200
Nobody cared for them.
Nobody missed them.

561
00:42:15,283 --> 00:42:20,872
