572
00:42:46,564 --> 00:42:50,819
Will that give you satisfaction, my son?

573
00:42:52,654 --> 00:42:57,659
Killing a helpless old fart?

574
00:42:58,660 --> 00:43:00,412
The killing, no.

575
00:43:00,495 --> 00:43:02,163
No satisfaction.

576
00:43:04,040 --> 00:43:08,169
Everything up until
the killing will be a gas.

577
00:43:11,339 --> 00:43:13,091
Kevin...

578
00:43:15,635 --> 00:43:17,971
...we're going home.

579
00:43:20,974 --> 00:43:23,977
You can scream now if you want to.

580
00:43:31,484 --> 00:43:36,281
<i>It's beautiful, Goldie.
It's just like I promised, only better.</i>

581
00:43:36,364 --> 00:43:39,367
<i>And when his eyes go dead,
the hell I sent him to</i>

582
00:43:39,451 --> 00:43:42,203
<i>must seem like heaven
after what I've done to him.</i>

583
00:43:43,204 --> 00:43:45,248
- Freeze!
- Oh, my God!

584
00:43:53,840 --> 00:43:54,799
<i>Jerks.</i>

585
00:43:54,883 --> 00:43:58,470
<i>They should've shot me in the head,
and enough times to make sure.</i>

586
00:43:58,553 --> 00:44:00,472
<i>It's so stupid.</i>

587
00:44:00,555 --> 00:44:04,517
<i>Everybody knows what's coming,
but they go through the motions anyway.</i>

588
00:44:04,601 --> 00:44:06,644
<i>What a waste of time.</i>

589
00:44:06,728 --> 00:44:11,316
<i>Months fall off the calendar
while I breathe and eat through tubes.</i>

590
00:44:11,399 --> 00:44:15,278
<i>Night after night, I wait for somebody
to come and finish me off.</i>

591
00:44:15,361 --> 00:44:19,073
<i>After a while, I realise
it's not gonna be so easy as that.</i>

592
00:44:20,158 --> 00:44:21,743
<i>I'm on my feet for ten minutes</i>

593
00:44:21,826 --> 00:44:24,829
<i>before the cops kick them out
from under me.</i>

594
00:44:24,913 --> 00:44:26,915
<i>They don't ask me any questions.</i>

595
00:44:26,998 --> 00:44:31,461
<i>They just keep knocking the crap out of
me and waving a confession in my face.</i>

596
00:44:31,544 --> 00:44:33,546
<i>And I keep spitting blood all over it</i>

597
00:44:33,630 --> 00:44:37,133
<i>and laughing at how many fresh copies
they come up with.</i>

598
00:44:37,217 --> 00:44:40,512
<i>Then along comes this worm
assistant district attorney</i>

599
00:44:40,595 --> 00:44:44,349
<i>who turns the recorder off and says
if I don't sign their confession,</i>

600
00:44:44,432 --> 00:44:46,184
<i>they'll kill my mom.</i>

601
00:44:46,267 --> 00:44:49,812
<i>I break his arm in three places
and I sign it.</i>

602
00:44:49,896 --> 00:44:52,857
<i>From then on, it's the circus
everybody wants it to be.</i>

603
00:44:53,524 --> 00:44:57,362
<i>They nail me for the works,
not just the people I did kill,</i>

604
00:44:57,445 --> 00:45:01,866
<i>but even Lucille and the girls
that Roark and Kevin ate,</i>

605
00:45:01,950 --> 00:45:04,202
<i>and even Goldie.</i>

606
00:45:04,285 --> 00:45:09,499
<i>The judge is all fire and brimstone
when she hands down the sentence.</i>

607
00:45:10,667 --> 00:45:13,670
<i>Midnight and my death
are only a few hours away,</i>

608
00:45:13,753 --> 00:45:16,756
<i>when I get my first surprise
in 18 months.</i>

609
00:45:18,508 --> 00:45:20,885
<i>My only visitor.</i>

610
00:45:20,969 --> 00:45:23,846
<i>I'm ready for anything but that scent.</i>

611
00:45:23,930 --> 00:45:27,183
I got 'em for you good,
didn't I, Goldie?

612
00:45:32,313 --> 00:45:34,816
Oh, I'm sorry, Wendy.

613
00:45:34,899 --> 00:45:38,236
I... I got confused again.

614
00:45:38,319 --> 00:45:40,989
Just seeing you like this.

615
00:45:43,283 --> 00:45:45,743
You can call me Goldie.

616
00:45:54,836 --> 00:45:57,839
<i>She smells like angels ought to smell.</i>

617
00:45:57,922 --> 00:46:00,675
<i>The perfect woman.</i>

618
00:46:00,758 --> 00:46:02,552
<i>The goddess.</i>

619
00:46:03,845 --> 00:46:06,055
<i>Goldie.</i>

620
00:46:06,139 --> 00:46:08,725
<i>She says her name is Goldie.</i>

621
00:46:11,352 --> 00:46:14,897
<i>They fix me a pretty decent steak
for my last meal.</i>

622
00:46:14,981 --> 00:46:19,444
<i>They even throw in a brew. It's the
first I've had since back at Nancy's.</i>

623
00:46:19,527 --> 00:46:24,240
<i>Then they shave my head and fix me
with a rubber diaper and get to it.</i>

624
00:46:24,324 --> 00:46:27,118
<i>And it's about damned time,
if you ask me.</i>

625
00:46:27,201 --> 00:46:29,912
"Though I walk through
the valley of the shadow..."

626
00:46:29,996 --> 00:46:32,623
Would you get a move on?
I haven't got all night.

627
00:46:32,707 --> 00:46:35,335
You heard the man. Hit it.

628
00:46:44,552 --> 00:46:47,638
Is that the best you can do,
you pansies?

629
00:47:00,860 --> 00:47:01,986
He's gone.

630
00:47:20,463 --> 00:47:24,300
Forget it, man. You can bang
on that door all night if you want to.

631
00:47:24,384 --> 00:47:26,928
