and get help,

649
00:48:20,940 --> 00:48:24,110
like... a shrink.

650
00:48:24,193 --> 00:48:27,572
Get help and get lost.

651
00:48:27,655 --> 00:48:28,906
Just open the door.

652
00:48:28,990 --> 00:48:33,870
Go ahead and open the door, Shellie.
I'll take care of this.

653
00:48:33,953 --> 00:48:38,040
