1271
01:31:37,659 --> 01:31:40,954
<i>They want a confession.
They won't get it.</i>

1272
01:31:44,165 --> 01:31:47,919
<i>There's a letter from Nancy waiting
when they put me in solitary.</i>

1273
01:31:48,003 --> 01:31:51,089
