1303
01:33:34,693 --> 01:33:36,778
<i>He stinks so bad, I want to throw up.</i>

1304
01:33:47,789 --> 01:33:50,667
<i>Practically knocked my head off
the bastard.</i>

1305
01:33:51,418 --> 01:33:53,712
