1364
01:38:06,589 --> 01:38:10,218
<i>Nancy Callahan, 19 years old.</i>

1365
01:38:12,136 --> 01:38:15,223
<i>And here I was,
expecting a skinny little bookworm,</i>

1366
01:38:15,306 --> 01:38:19,060
<i>maybe a bit too shy for her own good.</i>

1367
01:38:19,143 --> 01:38:24,941
<i>How little she told me about herself
in all her letters for all those years.</i>

1368
01:38:29,237 --> 01:38:31,656
<i>How the hell did they find her?</i>

1369
01:38:31,739 --> 01:38:34,242
<i>Then it hits me.</i>

1370
01:38:34,325 --> 01:38:36,452
<i>They were bluffing.</i>

1371
01:38:37,412 --> 01:38:40,331
<i>I've led them straight to her.</i>

1372
01:38:48,589 --> 01:38:51,634
<i>She hasn't spotted you yet.</i>

1373
01:38:51,718 --> 01:38:54,262
<i>Turn around and walk out the door.</i>

1374
01:38:55,388 --> 01:38:56,931
<i>Lead the creep outside.</i>

1375
01:38:57,014 --> 01:39:02,395
