if you sit down.

1432
01:43:17,775 --> 01:43:20,903
<i>I've never been all that good
with people.</i>

1433
01:43:20,986 --> 01:43:24,323
<i>When it comes to reassuring
a traumatised 19-year-old,</i>

1434
01:43:24,407 --> 01:43:28,285
